1. *Makar* je to bila zajebancija, moramo je poštovati (At least it was a joke, we have to respect it).
2. *Makar* se čini da je sve u redu, treba još malo proveriti (At least it seems that everything is ok, we still need to check it).
3. Nismo imali dovoljno vremena, ali smo uspeli učiniti *makar* malo (We didn't have enough time, but we managed to do at least a little).
4. Još uvek nismo postigli pravo rešenje, ali *makar* smo pronašli neka privremena rešenja (We still haven't achieved the right solution, but at least we've found some temporary solutions).
5. Ako ne uspemo da ostvarimo svoj cilj, *makar* ćemo biti srećni što smo pokušali (If we don't succeed in achieving our goal, at least we'll be happy that we tried).